-1.title: Episode dated 5 September 2008
-1.plot: Fort Campbell, Kentucky: Two helicopters on a training exercise collide; North Hollywood, California: Police officers battle two heavily armed bank robbers in a 44-minute gun battle; Stockton, California: A canopy being constructed for an outdoor concert collapses during a strong wind gust; White Rock, Canada: A motorized para-glider crashes into power lines.

1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Amsterdam, New York: A fire fighter is caught in a house explosion. Passengers escape a 737 fire and explosion. Okinawa: A couple survives in a tornado resistant house. Gulf of Tonkin, Vietnam: A missile is accidentally launched on the fight deck of the USS Forestall. Jefferson, Georgia: Family members see their loved ones in a car race crash. A rescue helicopter crashes on Mount Hood.

2.title: Air Show Crash
2.plot: An F-18 Hornet Marine pilot survives a 75 G crash. A Firefighter falls into a burning pool of diesel fuel. A raging river undermines the foundations of several houses and destroys them. A crane topples during the erection of a water tower causing two workmen to fall over 100 feet and observers to scatter. Two police officers barely survive the explosion of a distraught suicidal bomber. An ammonium perchlorate fire at a rocket fuel plant results in a massive explosion.

3.title: News Chopper Goes Down
3.plot: News chopper goes down; Snake-eye Bomb hits A-4 Skyhawk; Grain silo collapses on tractor; Drag Race Crash; Fireworks explosion; helicopter crane rescue.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Persian Gulf, USS Theodore Roosevelt: An aircraft carrier crewman survives being sucked into a jet engine. South Africa, Indian Ocean: The captain and crew abandon sinking cruise ship loaded with passengers. El Mirage, California: A motorcycle rider is dragged behind his bike at near world record speed and crashes again two weeks later. Comoros Islands: A pilot ditches his hijacked 767 at sea near a beach when the plane runs out of fuel. Three Rivers, Texas: A burning oil tank explodes.

5.title: Tail Rotor Fails
5.plot: Milwaukee, Wisconson: A chopper pilot carrying a 3400-pound air conditioning unit crashes after his tail rotor stops spinning; Ennis, Texas: A drag racer t-bones another at 200 mph; Tucson, Arizona: Three men are trapped in a flash flood in a previously dry creek bed; USS Kitty Hawk: Two pilots have to eject from a fighter jet that crashes onto the carrier deck; Poipu, Hawaii: A family rides out Hurricane Iniki while part of their house crashes around them.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: A man standing in the water on the edge of Niagra Falls contemplates suicide. A drag boat racer rolls and disintegrates. A volcanic eruption devastates Plymouth, Montserrat. An elderly couple is rescued from flood waters by helicopter, An experimental airship, the Helistat, shakes apart. A kite surfer is swept 300 feet into the air by and updraft.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: Clinton Township, Michigan: A magician's escape stunt goes wrong when he falls into the river after flames burn his rope; Sioux City, Iowa: United Flight 232; Rantoul, Illinois: A skydiver's chute opens too soon and gets snagged on the airplane's tail; Bowling Green, Kentucky: A man being pursued by cops holes up inside his former employer's house after ramming git with his car; Portland, Oregon: Two men in a truck have to outrace an oncoming mud slide.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: A fishing boat flounders in the ice choked Bering sea. Riders collide in a jet ski race. An ejection seat malfunction results in an navy airman precariously caught half way out of his cockpit. A man with a long standing grudge goes on a rampage in an armored bulldozer. Finally, Shockware provides a close up look at one of California's devastating forest fires.

9.title: Episode #1.9
9.plot: Murdock, Illinois: Tank cars full of liquid propane and other volatile chemicals explode following a train crash. Daytona, Florida: A rescue worker is tossed into the air when an out of control race car ventures into the infield. Cook Inlet, Alaska: A Coast Guard helicopter comes to the rescue as a fishing boat sinks in frigid Alaskan waters. Cornwall, England: A world famous ATV stunt driver crashes when he can't get enough speed for his jump over a paddle-wheel boat. Cape Canaveral, Florida: A Delta 2 rocket experiences an anomaly after rising 2000 feet.

10.title: Episode #1.10
10.plot: Englishtown, New Jersey: A funny car driver is knocked unconscious in a crash but his car drives on out of control. Cerro Negro, Nicaragua: A down hill biker crashes and rolls down a volcano when his bike breaks apart. Ontario, Canada: A boat crashes into a draw bridge and floats away out of control and burning. USS America, Mediterranean Sea: A pilot ejects from the deck of an aircraft carrier when his tale hook malfunctions. Oahu, Hawaii: A large wave sweeps a man out to sea and into a cave.

11.title: Episode #1.11
11.plot: A midget car crashes, spills methanol and nearly burns the driver alive. A sinkhole caused by faulty sewer work swallows a million dollar house. A jet boat goes airborne and crashes. A pregnant skydiver goes into a spin and lands on her face in a parking lot. A rescue helicopter crashes in a canyon then fire erupts while a man is pinned underneath.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: A time bomb explodes in a bomb squad officer's face. A skydiver gets snagged in the airplanes landing gear. A motorcyclist's jump is just a little bit short. A skier tumbles down a rock strewn mountain. A practice motorcycle jump ends on a bulldozer. A city worker is sucked into a sewer pipe.

13.title: Episode #1.13
13.plot: Boston, Massachusetts: A bomb explodes near a bomb technicians face; Dunbar, Pennsylvania: A skydiver's suit gets snagged on the airplane's landing gear; Del Mar, California: A daredevil attempting to jump over 22 cars crashes on the landing ramp; Valdez, Alaska: A skier falls 600 feet down a mountain; Anne Arundel, Maryland: A dirt biker attempting a 360 comes off his bike and crashes onto a tractor parked beside his intended landing area; Brisbane, Australia: A maintenance worker gets caught in a storm drain that had been clogged up in a recent storm.

20.plot: Oceanside, Californa: A wheel of a CH-46 Sea Knight catches the edge of a ship during a training exercise, causing it to lose control and drop into the water; Oklahoma City: An 18-year-old woman crashes near a burning tanker truck carrying 9000 gallons of fuel, and can't see how to get out of the inferno because of all the thick, black smoke; Lake Austin, Texas: Boaters in a boat with a stalled engine are headed toward a dam with a 60-foot drop; St. Lawrence River, Canada: A man attempts to fly a rocket-powered Lincoln across the St. Lawrence River; Liberty Island, ...

22.title: Episode #1.22
22.plot: Moreton Bay, Australia: A barge that is being sunk to form an artificial reef explodes with much greater force than expected; Dayton, Ohio: A man and his grandson crash in a home-built airplane; Sandy Springs, Georgia: A bomb explodes outside a professional office building; Waialua, Hawaii: A utility worker rushes to save a helicopter pilot who has crashed into an irrigation canal; Corsica, France: A mountain kayaker comes out of his kayak and is trapped in the churning wake below a waterfall.

27.title: Landing Gear Stuck
27.plot: St. Augustine, Florida: A Piper Turbo is in danger of crashing when one of its landing gear gets stuck in the wheel well; Honolulu, Hawaii: A 21-year-old African elephant goes on a rampage; Cedar Valley, Utah: A helicopter pilot attempting a loop crashes; Santa Fe, Argentina: A bus goes off a bridge after a car crashes into it; Plymouth, England: Two boat racers have to escape from their overturned speedboat after it wipes out at 270 kph.

28.title: Ford Trimotor Crash
28.plot: Fullerton, California: A replica of a 1930s Ford Trimotor crashes in front of a crowd; Salt Lake City, Utah: A motorist who has skidded of the road from a patch of black ice is struck by a rock band's van that has hit the same patch; An EA-6 Prowler crashes into S-3 Viking about the carrier USS Enterprise; Assisi, Italy: Inspectors in a church damaged by a quake are surprised when an aftershock causes a roof fall; Sydney, Australia: A surf boat crashes into another.

1.title: Stunt Plane Crash
1.plot: Salina, California: A stunt plane crashes coming in for a landing. Crested Butte, Colorado: A snowmobiler is crushed beneath another snowmobile. Hagerstown, Maryland:: A racer crashes into a wall. Mexico City, Mexico: An escape artist is severely burned when a stunt explodes prematurely. Fort Lauderdale, Florida: A sight-seeing boat starts sinking after another boat swamps it.

imdb.title: Shockwave
plot: The cause of some of the most dramatic disasters ever caught on tape are explained.::David Foss
